name: Materal Design for desktop - Dashboard UI kit
description:
Figma library with dashboard templates based on reusable desktop app patterns carefully handpicked from the most popular products. Contains 550+ components and 48 desktop templates (light and dark) in 1440px width each. You can remix and transform layouts according to your design mission. This asset helps to create better dashboards as it covers a wide range of ready-to-use templates.
